  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-AR-02 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Multiple credibility factors achieve levels far below required levels, yet the decision record records Accepted — a direct rebutting defeater (W-AR-02).",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/morrison-cou2-hemolysis-requirement",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/morrison-cou2-hemolysis-claim",
