      "acceptanceCriteria": "Rigorous code verification against analytic solutions or highly refined benchmarks required for all relevant physics modules.",
      "rationale": "Code verification was performed only for simple pipe-flow benchmarks; rotating-zone and hemolysis transport modules were not verified. Achieved level 2 is two steps below required level 4."
