      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal Richardson extrapolation or equivalent with GCI reported for all QoIs at all operating points.",
      "rationale": "A single three-level mesh refinement study was performed at one operating point; GCI was not reported and extrapolation was not applied to hemolysis index. Achieved level 2 is three steps below required level 5."
