      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must span the full COU operating envelope including all flow-speed combinations at VAD conditions.",
      "rationale": "Validation was conducted on a benchtop mock loop at reduced speed; VAD-representative rotational speeds and patient flow conditions were not tested. Achieved level 2 is three steps below required level 5."
    },
