      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence must be demonstrated to machine-precision tolerances with residual history documented for all simulations.",
      "rationale": "Residual convergence was checked only for continuity and momentum; hemolysis transport equation residuals were not monitored and convergence was declared by wall-clock time. Achieved level 1 is three steps below required level 4."
