      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Full characterization and uncertainty quantification of all model input parameters required, including blood rheology and pump geometry tolerances.",
      "rationale": "Blood viscosity was assumed Newtonian at a single nominal value; pump geometry tolerances from manufacturing were not incorporated. Factor not assessed; epistemic gap flagged at MRL 5."
    },
