      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental samples must be representative of patient-use blood with documented anticoagulation protocol and sample variability characterization.",
      "rationale": "Experimental hemolysis data used bovine blood without characterization of inter-sample variability or anticoagulation protocol documentation. Factor not assessed; epistemic gap flagged at MRL 5."
